0.title: Catching Kelce Preview Special
0.plot: Meet superstar tight end, Travis Kelce, as he prepares to find love. From his goofy personality, sexy smile and crazy sense of humor, you'll root for him even if you don't root for the team he plays for! See casting tapes of rejects, meet some of the lucky girls that made the show and enjoy a sneak peek at the wild ride to come on this season of Catching Kelce!

1.title: 50 Girls, 1 Tight End
1.plot: In the series premiere, NFL superstar tight end Travis Kelce is looking for love and 50 WOMEN - 1 from every US State - have shown up to fight for him. With limited time to make their mark on Travis, and two shocking eliminations, the competition between the girls heats up quickly.

2.title: Let the Games Begin
2.plot: With 15 girls remaining, Travis reveals that each week he'll invite one girl on a group date, but it's up to HER who comes along with. Ass kissing, alliances and strategies quickly come into play while Travis begins to form connections with the girls.

3.title: A Novel Romance
3.plot: After playing in a down and dirty football game, 4 lucky girls get glam and head to a star-studded, red-carpet event with Travis. One girl's dating past comes back to haunt her, and beef between girls hits a boiling point in a dramatic elimination.

4.title: Backstabbing Besties
4.plot: Travis brings 4 girls to a video game shoot where they form strong virtual connections. When the girls aren't happy about his choice for the solo date, they decide to confront Travis about his decision risking being sent home themselves.

5.title: Romance at Red Foo's
5.plot: The girls picked for the group date get a big surprise when they are invited to the Party Rock Mansion. After too many shots, some connections grow stronger while others stumble. Meanwhile former best friends face off in elimination with an outcome no one saw coming.

6.title: Walk of Shame
6.plot: Six remain as Travis takes four lucky girls on the All Access Group date to see WAG Jesse James Decker rock at the world famous Roxy. Meanwhile a plot by two girls to take out their competition backfires. Travis invites one girl back to his place for the VIP solo date and the other girls can't stand the suspense... is it a nightcap... or a sleepover?

7.title: Who Caught Kelce?
7.plot: In the dramatic 2-hour season finale, Travis takes his final 4 girls on a yacht to relax and let loose on their final group date. But after a day of partying things get serious fast when he reveals that one of them will be going home that night. After an emotional elimination, Travis brings the final three on a private jet to Kansas City so he can see how they'll handle his life outside of LA. From 50 women down to 1. Who will catch Kelce?

imdb.plot outline: American football player Travis Kelce is known for catching passes as a tight end for the Kansas City Chiefs. As a pro football star and an eligible bachelor, Kelce is quite the catch himself. In the dating competition series "Catching Kelce," 50 women from 50 states vie to win the heart of the pro football player. With help from his famous friends and family, Kelce attempts to find the woman who will become his perfect teammate.
